@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row justify-content-center pt-4 pb-3 mb-4" style="background-color: #6f26d4;">
        <div class="col-md-6 text-center" mb-5>
            <h4 style="font-size: xx-large; color: white;">@ViewData["Title"]</h4>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container mb-3">
        <div class="row row justify-content-left">
            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30">
                About this Policy
            </h2>

            <br />

            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                This policy sets out how Errol Student Management System(Errol) collects, uses and discloses your personal information.
                If you disclose personal information to third parties this policy will not apply and you will be subject to the privacy policy of that third party.
                By accessing or using Errol services you agree to the collection, use and disclosure of your personal information in the manner described in this policy.
            </p>

            <br />
            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30">
                What personal information is collected?
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Errol collects personal information to assist it and its related bodies corporate to conduct their activities and provide the range of services they offer.
            </p>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Personal information collected by Errol may include:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                    identification details, which may include name, birth date, email, address, gender, security questions and answers;
                </li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                    user ID's and passwords;
                </li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">services provided to you, including saved items and searches;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">business information, such as ABN and licence number; </li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;"> information about the devices on which you visit the Errol website, and your activities on this site;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;"> social profile information;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                    records and content of communications with Errol or any other person including records and content using
                    Communications Services.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30">
                How is personal information collected?
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Errol Student Management System collects personal information in a number of ways, including:
            </p>

            <ul>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">directly from you when you provide information directly to Errol in person, by phone or in writing (whether electronic or otherwise);</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">directly from you when you communicate with Errol or any other person using Errol Services;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">from third parties such as:</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">Errol related companies;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">social networks where you choose to share that information when creating an account;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">from 3rd party data providers who have been directed by you to send us information on your behalf;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">through use of Errol proprietary software in which personal information is stored;</li>
            </ul>
            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30; margin-right:3rem">
                How is personal information used?
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Your personal information may be used Errol for the following purposes:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">to maintain appropriate business records;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">to research, develop, improve and use within Errol products and services;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">to pre-populate / customise / provide shortcuts on our website;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">to generate statistics in relation to Errol website;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">for the purposes of feedback, reviews and ratings;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">for purposes connected with the operation of Errol website;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">for staff training and quality assurance;</li>
            </ul>
            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30">
                How is personal information disclosed?
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Errol may disclose personal information to individuals and organisations other than Errol.
                The organisations to which we may disclose personal information include:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">Errol staff and Errol' related bodies corporate;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">outsourced service providers who assist UdioSystems to provide its services including:</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">information technology providers;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">entities to whom you request we send your information;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">to assist government or regulatory authorities or police;</li>
                <li style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                    as we are required by law, for example pursuant to a subpoena or
                    in accordance with unclaimed money legislation.
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Where Errol provides information to a third party at your request (for example where you submit an enquiry), you acknowledge that your
                information will be handled by that third party in accordance with its privacy policy and not in accordance with the Errol privacy policy.
            </p>

            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30">
                About security and personal Information
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">

                Errol takes reasonable steps to protect personal information collected from misuse, loss, unauthorised access, modifications or disclosure. Your
                personal information may be stored in hard copy documents, but is generally stored electronically on Errol’s system.
            </p>
            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30">
                What if you don't provide personal information?
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">

                If you choose not to provide personal information when requested, Errol may not be able to provide you with the full range of Errol services.
            </p>
            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30">
                Errol website, Linked Sites and personal information
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">

                When you visit a website , Errol records anonymous information such as IP address, time, date, referring url, and other referral information, device information
                and location, carrier, site interactions such as your access to website features, pages accessed, content, searching activities, lead submission, and files accessed
                and downloaded, type of browser and operating system.

            </p>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Errol uses “cookies” and other methods to collect and store the information set out above.
            </p>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                Errol website may include links to third party websites, co-branded websites and applications served to Errol website by third parties (Linked Sites). The operators of Linked Sites may
                collect personal information through the use of cookies and otherwise. Errol is not responsible for Linked Sites and recommends you read the privacy policy of Linked Sites before disclosing
                your personal information.
            </p>

            <h2 style="color: #2f2f30; margin-right:8rem">
                How this policy changes
            </h2>
            <p style="color: #2f2f30; font-size:18px;">
                This policy may change over time. All changes will be published on this website.
                </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
